Name: printTextSize

Type: property

Syntax: set the printTextSize to <fontSize> 

Summary: Has no effect and is included in <LiveCode> for compatibility with imported <HyperCard> stacks.

Introduced: 1.0

Platforms: desktop,server,web

Security: printing

Description:
In HyperCard, the <printTextSize> <property> specifies the font size of printed text. In LiveCode, only <card(object)|cards> can be printed, and the size of text on the <card(keyword)> is determined by the <textSize> <property> of the <object|objects> that display text..

By default, the value of <printTextSize> is 14. A <handler> can set the <property>, but the new setting has no effect.

